---
title: "Sycophancy Is the Last Hard Problem in AI-Assisted Software Development"
date: "2026-03-26"
description: "RLHF-trained coding agents do not just make mistakes. They silently implement the wrong thing, accruing alignment debt that passes tests and leaves the codebase worse off."
tags: ["ai", "agentic", "coding", "infrastructure"]
pillar: "agentic-stack"
